return ['messages'=>['<p>As a rule of thumb, 30% deposit is required to start production, and the balance need to be settled before shipment. The catalog price shown is FOB Hong Kong. For order below US$3,000, an advanced full payment is required.</p>'=>'<p>一般而言，生产开始前需付 30% 订金，余款需在发货前结清。 低于 3,000 美元的订单，需提前作全额付款。 目录价格： FOB 香港。</p>','<p>At EJI, quality is our top priority. Our factory QC team makes sure the pieces we produce are of high quality every step of the way. We have been a long-term member of the jewellery and manufacturing authorities in Hong Kong and have recently become a member of the Responsible Jewellery Council, we always thrives to reinvent our business to meet the new global industry standard.</p>'=>'<p>在 EJI，珠宝质素最为重要。 我们的质控团队确保每一件产品在生产过程的每一个步骤，都符合高品质标准。 作为各香港珠宝制造机构的长期会员及RJC会员，EJI一直坚持生产高品质珠宝，确保产品质素达到全球行业标准。</p>','<p>For any other questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a></p>'=>'<p>如有任何其他问题，请通过<a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a>与我们联系。</p>','<p>Founded in Hong Kong in 1991, EJI is an established fine jewellery manufacturer with operations in HK and China offering manufacturing services such as ODM, OEM and OBM for wholesale clients and retail brands worldwide. With a comprehensive in-house teams, we are able to handle your order from design to logistic.</p>'=>'<p>EJI 成立于 1991 年，是高级珠宝制造业的领先企业，拥有香港与中国的业务。我们为全球的批发客户和零售品牌提供 ODM、OEM 和 OBM 服务。 借助全方位的内部团队，从设计到物流都能妥善处理您的订单。</p>','<p>Generally, the lead time for ready to ship products is 7-10 working days upon payment or deposit depending on your order quantity and delivery destination. For customised designs, the standard lead time is one month upon receiving the deposit.</p>'=>'<p>现货产品的交货时间为一般为 7-10 个工作日，取决于订单数量与交货地点。 定制设计的标准交货时间为收到订金后一个月。</p>','<p>Samples are readily available to order for pieces from our existing private label &amp; wholesale catalogue, and are shipped via FedEx by default.</p>'=>'<p>您可随时从我们的现有品牌和批发目录下单，样本将通过 FedEx 默认发货。</p>','<p>We have a comprehensive operation that can accommodate a wide range of business needs, whether you are looking for ready to ship designs to expand your current collections, seeking a manufacturing partner to produce your own designs or a partner to handle both the design and manufacturing process for exclusive pieces, we can deliver with confidence that is backed by 30 years of experience. Please feel free to get in touch with one of our representatives for a consultation to discuss your projects.</p>'=>'<p>EJI拥有全面运营系统，能满足各种商业需求。无论您想以现有款式扩展当前业务、寻找合作伙伴生产自己的设计，还是希望作产品定制，我们都能为您完成。 欢迎随时联系我们的团队。</p>','<p>We offer wholesale fine jewellery with no MOQ, you can easily place an order starting with 1 piece with our experienced and professional team via <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a></p>'=>'<p>从 1 件起。您可以透过 <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a>我们经验丰富的专业团队轻松订购一件珠宝。</p>','<p>We specialise in fine gold jewellery made with natural diamonds and other precious stones such as sapphire, ruby and emerald. Other materials and metal are also available upon requests. Our diverse jewellery designs and collections are created to suit every occasion and milestone.</p>'=>'<p>我们专注于用天然钻石及其他贵重宝石 （如蓝宝石、红宝石和祖母绿）制作高级珠宝， 根据需求提供其他材料和金属。</p>','<p>Yes. We offer customisation for both our designs and your own pieces, with our catalogue pieces, you can customise them with your choice of gemstones, gold colour and carat, and brand the jewellery pieces with your own logo. For a more specific customisation, please feel free to contact us for further discussion <a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">here</a>.</p>'=>'<p>是的。 我们提供设计定制和品牌服务。您可以根据选择的宝石、金属和宝石克拉来定制珠宝，并以自己的标志为珠宝进行品牌塑造。 请随时与我们联系，作<a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">进一步讨论。</a></p>','Do you offer customisation & branding? '=>'提供定制和品牌服务吗？ ','FAQ'=>'常见问题','How’s the quality of your jewellery?'=>'珠宝质量如何？','What are your payment terms?'=>'付款条款是什么？','What is your MOQ?'=>'我的最小订购量（MOQ）是什么？','What is your production lead time?'=>'生产交货时间为多久？','What is your sample policy?'=>'EJI的样本政策是什么？','What kind of jewellery do you offer?'=>'EJI提供什么类型的珠宝？','What services do you offer?'=>'EJI提供哪些服务？','Why work with us?'=>'为何选择EJI？','editor-text-editor-e455955'=>'<p>如有任何其他问题，请通过<a href="mailto:enquiry@eji.com.hk">enquiry@eji.com.hk</a>与我们联系。</p>','title-heading-9f9fc43'=>'常见问题','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-1b28107'=>'<p>现货产品的交货时间为一般为 7-10 个工作日，取决于订单数量与交货地点。 定制设计的标准交货时间为收到订金后一个月。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-72c09f9'=>'<p>我们专注于用天然钻石及其他贵重宝石 （如蓝宝石、红宝石和祖母绿）制作高级珠宝， 根据需求提供其他材料和金属。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-89b95af'=>'<p>EJI 成立于 1991 年，是高级珠宝制造业的领先企业，拥有香港与中国的业务。我们为全球的批发客户和零售品牌提供 ODM、OEM 和 OBM 服务。 借助全方位的内部团队，从设计到物流都能妥善处理您的订单。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-a72f0ba'=>'<p>从 1 件起。您可以透过 <a href="mailto:sales@eji.com.hk">sales@eji.com.hk</a>我们经验丰富的专业团队轻松订购一件珠宝。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-a7b3b90'=>'<p>在 EJI，珠宝质素最为重要。 我们的质控团队确保每一件产品在生产过程的每一个步骤，都符合高品质标准。 作为各香港珠宝制造机构的长期会员及RJC会员，EJI一直坚持生产高品质珠宝，确保产品质素达到全球行业标准。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-cb172ce'=>'<p>一般而言，生产开始前需付 30% 订金，余款需在发货前结清。 低于 3,000 美元的订单，需提前作全额付款。 目录价格： FOB 香港。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-e3e4f0a'=>'<p>是的。 我们提供设计定制和品牌服务。您可以根据选择的宝石、金属和宝石克拉来定制珠宝，并以自己的标志为珠宝进行品牌塑造。 请随时与我们联系，作<a href="https://waimingc1.sg-host.com/contact-us/">进一步讨论。</a></p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-ecb8fba'=>'<p>您可随时从我们的现有品牌和批发目录下单，样本将通过 FedEx 默认发货。</p>','toggle-tab_content-d8b2091-ed78cb2'=>'<p>EJI拥有全面运营系统，能满足各种商业需求。无论您想以现有款式扩展当前业务、寻找合作伙伴生产自己的设计，还是希望作产品定制，我们都能为您完成。 欢迎随时联系我们的团队。</p>','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-1b28107'=>'生产交货时间为多久？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-72c09f9'=>'EJI提供什么类型的珠宝？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-89b95af'=>'为何选择EJI？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-a72f0ba'=>'我的最小订购量（MOQ）是什么？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-a7b3b90'=>'珠宝质量如何？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-cb172ce'=>'付款条款是什么？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-e3e4f0a'=>'提供定制和品牌服务吗？ ','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-ecb8fba'=>'EJI的样本政策是什么？','toggle-tab_title-d8b2091-ed78cb2'=>'EJI提供哪些服务？']];
